## Success Metrics Dashboard

### Lead Generation:
- Total downloads per white paper
- Landing page conversion rate (target: 25-40%)
- Traffic sources
- Cost per lead (if using paid)

### Engagement:
- Email open rates (target: 40-50%)
- Click-through rates (target: 15-25%)
- Time on landing page
- Bounce rate

### Lead Quality:
- Lead-to-opportunity rate
- Lead source by white paper
- Job title distribution
- Company size distribution

### Business Impact:
- Opportunities created
- Pipeline value
- Closed deals attributed
- Customer lifetime value by source

### Content Performance:
- Most downloaded white papers
- Blog posts driving most traffic
- Best performing CTAs
- A/B test winners

